audio_descriptions.notes:
In a dark room, eight people dress up as different Disney Villains: Maleficent, Hades, Cruella de Vil, Jafar, that Evil Queen, Captain Hook, Ursula, and Scar. Each villain performs a different situation.
Scar stands in the middle of the room. Cut to black.

tags: snow white and the seven dwarfs
